                <note rend="inline" type="source">Secretary’s Daily Meetings, Lot 58 D 609<note
                        n="1" xml:id="d89fn1">Chronological collection of the records of the
                        Secretary of State’s Daily Meetings with top Department of State officials
                        for the years 1949–1952 as maintained by the Special Assistant to the
                        Secretary of State.</note>
                </note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Summary of Meeting With the Secretary of State</hi>
                    <note n="2" xml:id="d89fn2">Prepared by William J. McWilliams, Director of the
                        Executive Secretariat.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">[Extract] <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-05-03">May 3,
                            1951</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <table>
                        <row>
                            <cell rendition="#top #nowrap">Participants:</cell>
